title: Every Switch 2 Launch Game

author: GameSpot
description:
We went hands-on with Sleep Awake, the upcoming psychological horror game from Spec Ops: The Line director Cory Davis and Nine Inch Nails/Guns N' Roses musician Robin Finck. Blending surreal, first-person exploration with unnerving music and a terrifying no-sleep premise, Sleep Awake is part of Blumhouse Games' debut slate. In this preview, we break down the game's unique concept, trippy visuals, and early gameplay—plus why it's one of the most intriguing titles from Summer Game Fest 2025.
